arim|al-Karim]]\n[al-Kareem]\n| The Noble/ Bountiful/ Generous/ Precious/ Honored/ Benefactor ||[http://quran.com/27/40 27:40], [http://quran.com/82/6 82:6]||style=\"text-align:center;\" | D\n|-\n| {{Audio|43-ar-raqib.ogg|43|help=no}}|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''<big>\u0671\u0644\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0651\u0642\u0650\u064a\u0628\u064f</big>'''\n|<big>'''\\ \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u0642\u064a\u0628'''</big>\n<big>'''\u0627\u0644\u0631\u0642\u064a\u0628'''</big>\n|ar-Raqiyb/\n\nar-Raq\u012bb\n|[[Raq\u012bb|Ar-Raqib]]\n[Ar-Raqeeb]\n| The Watchful/ Observer/ Ever-Watchful/ Watcher ||[http://quran.com/4/1 4:1], [http://quran.com/5/117 5:117]||style=\"text-align:center;\" | D\n|-\n| {{Audio|44-al-mujib.ogg|44|help=no}}|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''<big>\u0671\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u062c\u0650\u064a\u0628\u064f</big>'''\n|<big>'''\u0627\u0644\u0645\u062c\u064a\u0628'''</big>\n|al-Mujiyb/\n\nal-Muj\u012bb\n|[[Mujib|al-Mujib]]\n[al-Mujiyb]\n| The Responsive/  Answerer/ Supreme Answerer/ Accepter of Invocation ||[http://quran.com/11/61 11:61]||style=\"text-align:center;\" | A\n|-\n| {{Audio|45-al-wasi.ogg|45|help=no}}|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''<big>\\* \u0671\u0644\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0670\u0633\u0650\u0639\u064f</big>'''\n'''<big>\u0671\u0644\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0650\u0639\u064f</big>'''\n\n[<big>'''*'''</big> = ''classical written form'']\n|<big>'''\\* \u0627\u0644\u0648\u0670\u0633\u0639'''</big>\n\n<big>'''\u0627\u0644\u0648\u0627\u0633\u0639'''</big>\n\n[<big>'''*'''</big> = ''classical written form'']\n|\u2019al-W\u0101si\u2018/\n\n\u2019al-W\u0101si\u2018\n|[[Al-W\u0101si\u02bf|al-Wasi\u2018/ al-Wasie]]\n[al-Waasi\u2018/ al-Waasie]\n| The Vast/ All-Embracing/ Omnipresent/ Boundless/ All-Encompassing ||[http://quran.com/2/268 2:268], [http://quran.com/3/73 3:73], [http://quran.com/5/54 5:54]||style=\"text-align:center;\" | A\n|-\n| {{Audio|46-al-hakim.ogg|46|help=no}}|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''<big>\u0671\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u06